{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "fa48e48d-4144-42b4-a37e-e17c61c22b36", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fa48e48d-4144-42b4-a37e-e17c61c22b36@1.pkg/1772597628177/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597628730", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/fa48e48d-4144-42b4-a37e-e17c61c22b36@1.pkg/1772597628177/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597628730"}, "identifier": "fa48e48d-4144-42b4-a37e-e17c61c22b36", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>本题考查维护国家安全的相关知识。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>A:专注经济建设是发展基础，但&ldquo;屏蔽外界干扰&rdquo;不符合实际需求，无法应对题干中的安全威胁，故A说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>B:加强国防建设能直接应对境外挑衅和分裂势力，是维护国家主权和领土完整的必要举措，故B符合题意。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span>C:我国坚持和平统一方针，武力并非当前解决台湾问题的首要选择，故C说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D:维护民族团结主要针对民族问题，而题干强调国家统一和外部势力威胁，故D不符合题意。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）近年来，国际形势波谲云诡，外部势力在台湾问题上频繁试探红线，南海区域的无端挑衅也时有发生。宗教极端势力、民族分裂势力以及国际恐怖势力等仍在暗处伺机而动，严重威胁我国安全与稳定。为此，我国应当（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）近年来，国际形势波谲云诡，外部势力在台湾问题上频繁试探红线，南海区域的无端挑衅也时有发生。宗教极端势力、民族分裂势力以及国际恐怖势力等仍在暗处伺机而动，严重威胁我国安全与稳定。为此，我国应当（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_typ